001package ltd.icecold.orangeengine.api.data.bone;
002
003public class Quaternion {
004    public float x;
005    public float y;
006    public float z;
007
008    public Quaternion() {
009    }
010
011    public Quaternion(float x, float y, float z) {
012        this.x = x;
013        this.y = y;
014        this.z = z;
015    }
016
017    @Override
018    public String toString() {
019        return "{" +
020                "x=" + x +
021                ", y=" + y +
022                ", z=" + z +
023                '}';
024    }
025}
